## Figma MCP integration (yd-design-system)

### Required flow
1. Run `get_design_context` for the exact node(s), then `get_screenshot` for visual reference.
2. If the response is truncated, use `get_metadata` and re-fetch only the needed nodes.
3. Translate React + Tailwind output into this repo's conventions before marking complete.

### Implementation
- UI components live in `packages/ui/src/components/`; export from `packages/ui/src/index.ts`.
- Design tokens live in `packages/tokens/`; prefer existing tokens over hardcoded values.
- Docs and examples live in `apps/docs-site/app/components/`.
- Reuse `@yd/ui` components (Button, Input, Select, Table, etc.) instead of duplicating markup.
- Match Figma visuals; resolve conflicts using design-system tokens from `packages/tokens`.
